General Information

Schick Xtreme 3 Sensitive for Women has 3 blades that flex and pivot to adapt to the curves of your body - thanks to an ergonomic handle with soft rubber grip for great control.

A conditioning strip with Aloe and Jojoba to deliver a luxuriously smooth shave. It's a great pick for women with sensitive skin. Flex To Your Curves

Suitable For: Sensitive

Boxed Contents: 4 Razors

Scent: Aloe & Jojoba

Warnings

Blades are sharp tools, please handle with care
Please keep the blade away from children
